Who: LORD ELDER, Kup
Location: The Ark - Command Center

> "Going to help"said Kup to lord Elder"If something happens me, send Elita to Lord Perseus's base, she will be safe there" the old autobot ran towards the exit.

Elder nodded as Kup rushed past him, insistent on rescuing Nightshift.
Elder furrowed his brows slightly and shook his head. "Be careful
Kup." Elder said over the Autobot's radio, "We don't want to add to
the Predacon's list of captives they seem to have growing over there."

Elder sighed as he commanded the shield to let Kup exit, closing it
almost as soon as the older Autobot cleared the field line. There was
something about that sensor ghost that still bugged him. He continued
to scan for it, as for a moment it appeared, and then before he could
get a weapons lock on it, disappeared again.

"Feldspar and rust!" Elder said in frustration.
